title: Rosetta Stone Speech Models + Engine  (Windows) v3.2.18
description:
*******************************************************************
Rosetta Stone Speech Models and Engine Installers (Windows) v3.2.18
*******************************************************************

Why install Rosetta Stone Speech Services?

Without the speech services installed, Learners will not be able to learn with the speech functions.
The functionality enabled by speech recognition is an integral part of the language learning experience.
Therefore, you should install the speech services before starting using Rosetta Stone.

Whatâ€™s included?

- Setup.exe for installing the speech engine on individual Windows computers
- RosettaStoneLtdServices.msi installer for remote deployment of speech engine to Windows computers
- RosettaStone_Models.exe for extracting specific language speech files
